HEADWORD: Filicoid
<hw>Fil"i*coid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>filix</ets>, <ets>-icis</ets>, fern + <ets>-oid</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>filicoi⟦ium⟧de</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Fernlike,
either in form or in the nature of the method of reproduction.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

